data.description: This house is not a drive-by! Walk into this spacious open floor plan and call it home! It is bright and open to the outdoors. You will enjoy an upgraded newer kitchen, completely remodeled in 2014 with maple cabinetry and hardwood floors leading out to a beautiful deck. The upstairs living room area is connected to the dining area for combination dinner and entertaining.The newly renovated bathroom is spa like with beautiful tile, new walls and a brand new vanity.(don't forget the bluetooth speaker in the shower)The two of three bedrooms are large and freshly painted and newly carpeted.The master suite is above and beyond spacious!This room is extra large with a vanity with a solid surface counter and full bathroom.The closet space is beyond what you would expect!Don't stop there!There is another bedroom, full bathroom and walk in closet overlooking the pool area.This would make a great nursery or work well as an office.Downstairs offers two living rooms each with wood fireplaces, an office space, a laundry room and half bath.The great room leads out to a two story deck and sitting area complete with an inground pool, huge yard and hot tub. Close to hospital, schools and shopping.
